## Commercial Use Guidelines

### Prohibited Without Permission:
- Commercial deployment of the WebPayback Protocol
- Use of "WebPayback" brand name or derivatives
- Listing on commercial platforms or marketplaces
- Monetization of the protocol or its derivatives
- Corporate or enterprise deployment

### Permitted Uses:
- Educational and research purposes
- Personal development and learning
- Non-commercial open source contributions
- Academic studies and analysis

### How to Request Commercial Permission:
For commercial use inquiries, please contact:
- Email: claudiob73@hotmail.com
- GitHub: Create an issue with "Commercial License Request" label
- Discord: Contact administrators in #business-inquiries

### Enforcement:
The WebPayback Protocol team reserves the right to enforce these restrictions and may take legal action against unauthorized commercial use.
